</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>If the payment method results in additional costs, enter the percentage value or flat rate value. The choice depends on the conditions of your contract. <strong>Important:</strong> Do not enter a value into both fields.<br>
For further information, refer to the <strong><a href="/en/basics/statistics">Statistics</a></strong> and <strong><a href="/en/basics/statistics/general-statistics/item/tops-flops">Tops/Flops</a></strong> pages of the manual. For an example for flat rate and percentage costs, refer to the <strong><a href="/en/order-processing/payment/managing-payment-methods#20">Basic settings</a></strong> page of the manual.</p>
