<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Amazon Payments payment method</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you want to use the payment method <strong>Amazon Payments</strong>, then do not create a separate Shopgate account for Amazon Payments. Use the account created in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
