<p>Set up an <strong><a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a></strong> to automatically send cancellations to Shopgate. Cancellations are handled as returns at Shopgate. Therefore, use the procedure <strong>Send return to Shopgate</strong>.</p>
